  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the safety and effectiveness of the combination of
      oxaliplatin and irinotecan (CPT-11) in patients with previously untreated, advanced small
      cell lung cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
